summary:
A mansion on the edge of a large lake. Fit with weapon rack, display case, and mannequin.
Very warm and homely. Small dock and well on the exterior. Interior is sunny and bright, an enchanting table and alchemy bench are located on the upper floor. On the exterior there is a small dock, well, and archery target for practice!
